Act as an expert web designer and developer. Create a clear, modern, and professional 5-page website for "BassyDue Construction & Engineering Ltd," a high-end residential and commercial construction firm. The website must be clean, scannable, and highly trustworthy.
Collaborate on a cohesive multi-page project
Give it a menu with drop down items linking the user to the different pages of the website


