Use Tailwind css to build the website
Let every page 


Page 2: About Us:
what to include:
● Page hero: 'About Us' with a background picture/image of a construction project,
● Company history and mission (3 paragraphs),
● Why you should work with Us: core values (safety, quality, integrity), 
● Meet the team section (4 photos and a brief bios of the leadership team),
● Awards or certifications (3 awards or certifications).


Page 3: Services:
What to include: 
Bulleted lists of capabilities: Pre-construction, General Contracting, Design-Build, and Remodeling. each list with icons and should be arranged in cards.


Page 4: Projects/Portfolio:
What to include:
● A grid layout showing high-quality images of recent completed projects, including project names, locations, and a short description of the work (3 completed projects).
● A grid layout showing high-quality images of a renovated projects, including project names, locations, and a short description of the work (2 renovated projects).
● A grid layout showing high-quality images of recent current projects under construction, including project names, locations, and a short description of the work (3 projects under construction).

Contact Us page: A location map, physical address, phone number, email address, and a lead-generation form for project inquiries.

Use Tailwind css to build the website
